PrecisOrder (a) setting apart land in Saskatchewan for the use and benefit of the SAULTEAUX BAND as Saulteaux Indian Reserves No. 159D (766.75 ha) and 159E (553.83 ha), and (b) consenting to the exercise by SASKATCHEWAN TELECOMMUNICATIONS of its power to take possession of an easement on those reserves, for the purposes of a telecommunications transmission system right-of-way.
